Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}黄昏交差点　駆け寄る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}“会いたい”と思う　そんな気持ちは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}空を泳いでる　雲みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}ぶつかって　溶けて　消えた？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}いつからだろう　すれ違ってる…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}それでも　とこかで　
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}あなただけ　求めて…いる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}会いたくて…　青空（そら）に描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}未来へと　続く　願い…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}今日もまた　こんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}眩しくて…　愛しくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}陽だまりに並んで咲いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.01,0:24:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}向日葵みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}見つめてたい　キラキラ　My Love
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}奔向黄昏时分的十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}想见你的心情就好像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}天空中飘浮的云朵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}互相碰撞 溶化 消失而去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}也不知从何时开始 我们彼此错过对方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}即便如此我也会在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}寻求着唯一的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.77,0:24:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}在蓝天画下了"想见你"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.31,0:24:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}期盼一直到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.07,0:24:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}今天也是那么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}让人眩晕 让人怜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.47,0:24:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}犹如向日葵一般
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.01,0:24:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}和阳光一起竞相开放
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an1\fad(500,500)\blur3}凝望着耀眼的　My Love
